reviewText: Not as explicit as I would have liked. It has the expected storyline for the story of Caligula but there was no visible penetration. Definitely not as hot as the original penthouse version but is a keeper for the library of those liking the genre.

A story of Caligula less explicitly-sexual than Caligula (Unrated Version) but enough transparent to understand a long way human rights and liberties made since the Roman Republic-an example of the best democracy of then barbaric ancient world, till nowadays.
